## install Cloudwatchangent____________
## 1. cd
## 2. wget https://s3.amazonaws.com/amazoncloudwatch-agent/linux/amd64/latest/AmazonCloudWatchAgent.zip
## 3. unzip AmazonCloudWatchAgent.zip 
## 4. sudo ./install.sh  >> creates a user and group for cloudwatchagent
## 5. vi cloudwatch-agent-config.json >> copy and paste congig line #
## 5.1 change the file path to the unstructured logs >>> "var/log/audit.log"
## 6. create a log group and no stream >> the agent creates it own 
# 7. sudo /opt/aws/amazon-cloudwatch-agent/bin/amazon-cloudwatch-agent-ctl -a fetch-config -m ec2 -c file:cloudwatch-agent-config.json -s 
# 7.1 it starts the cloudwatch agent and use config file that is present 
# 7.2 see the status of the agent >> sudo /opt/aws/amazon-cloudwatch-agent/bin/amazon-cloudwatch-agent-ctl -m ec2 -a status
# 7.3 is it running ?

